{"tid":1890030,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［嚴正警告］信報：知情者分析，黨鐵根據機制根本冇得加價，主動話凍結只係順水人情扮好人，仲可以用嚟講租金時討價還價！！","createTime":"2020-02-21T02:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T05:25:50.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ae4b82e9b3406f4b270f2545196d2ab2d9ea644a","tid":1890030,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:59:49.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯知情者分析，港鐵所謂凍結八達通票價只是虛晃一招，事關按照「可加可減機制」，關鍵因素之一的綜合消費物價指數變動，去年底起已隨經濟走下坡呈現跌幅。港鐵明顯「計過度過」，深明在這個計算辦法下，難有理據提出加價。<br />\n<br />\n既然調高收費無望，倒不如來個順水人情，主動宣告凍結票價，一方面能營造抗疫時期同舟共濟的良心企業形象，另一方面留有一手，倘若日後港鐵旗下物業商戶再要求減租，可憑此事跟商戶討價還價，呼籲齊齊共渡時艱。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2382730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2382730&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVN5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=ef8c56c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2382730</a>"},{"pid":"cdd769d220b71faf77ae262171776dfd893cffd1","tid":1890030,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T03:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sxPBdyF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsxPBdyF.jpg&h=fae66d63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02338af91b9e51d057580b8d3bf2117a714a0564","tid":1890030,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T03:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d0583fd05b148268b0d9f752964b14d0a73e8a","tid":1890030,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:23:37.000Z","msg":"想問下個「生產力因素」有無關係？匪鐵生產力越來越低，應該減價喎"},{"pid":"d666375bbb0a01ba0bdafe53df2fd5d9d259f4e6","tid":1890030,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3d0583fd05b148268b0d9f752964b14d0a73e8a","tid":1890030,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:23:37.000Z","msg":"想問下個「生產力因素」有無關係？匪鐵